Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.04,0:00:04.98,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,470)}School Rumble is coming up next!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.92,0:00:21.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s supposed to be around here…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.95,0:00:28.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.50,0:00:38.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,3,559.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.44,0:00:43.84,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You must transfer all the\Nwater in the jug without spilling a drop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.41,0:00:48.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What an intensive training.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.26,0:00:52.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But… something’s different.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.12,0:00:54.15,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not the usual composed Hanai!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.79,0:00:57.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What could have happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:00:58.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:02.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, he has the\Npower of a drawn sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.89,0:01:06.35,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes… He has lost the scabbard of reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.56,0:01:08.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,A beast starving for blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.90,0:01:14.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,In his heart, he is… battling evil itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.58,0:01:22.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lose yourself and you\Ncannot conquer your path.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.41,0:01:25.52,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,However, with love a man becomes strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.81,0:01:27.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a thing beyond our control.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:31.69,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, putting this matter off…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.39,0:01:34.26,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to drop him,\Nnow is the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.09,0:01:36.70,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I’m not here for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.93,0:01:41.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You are strong but unable to show\Nyour feminine side, isn’t that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:44.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He is one that can understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.11,0:01:49.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Suou? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:52.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you haven’t been\Nhome for two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.78,0:01:55.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Two days… Has it only been that long?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.53,0:01:58.59,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I’ve been here half a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:02.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, who was\Nthat old man just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.17,0:02:05.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,A stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:06.98,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:08.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know you mustn’t go off by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.34,0:02:11.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, now is the time for you, too, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.23,0:02:12.98,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! I am Akiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:13.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Akemi-san!
