Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:27.22,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s something I want to tell you, but it’s too heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:33.10,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like this, it seems I must break
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:42.29,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,There are too many of these indescribable feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:49.13,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot deliver them to you, though you are near, the distance is great
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:57.95,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever only looking up at the blue sky is no good
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.95,0:03:05.18,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Spinning around (spinning around)…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:12.59,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Unsteadily mustering strength, I want to try diving into your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.59,0:03:19.72,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Spinning around (spinning around)…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.12,0:03:29.21,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightly floating, again today I am alone above the clouds
