Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:04:00.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That Suou… Why did she hit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:06.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But… downtown hasn’t changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:08.68,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s so cool…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:12.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely the best in our school!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.22,0:04:14.65,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Those sunglasses look so sinister, it’s great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:17.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Students from my school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:21.56,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Would a kiss be okay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.44,0:04:25.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.73,0:04:29.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he has a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.07,0:04:30.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’d like to go out with him one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:33.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,With Harima Kenji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:38.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:41.80,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me all what you were talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:47.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,In… in the alley behind the coffee shop\Nwe were picked on by some delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:48.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He helped us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:50.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he’s still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:51.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:54.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that’s it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:55.77,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that’s what it’s all about!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:59.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakumo-kun must have been\Ndeceived in the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:03.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And, I think… it was all an act!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.37,0:05:06.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t permit it! Harima Kenji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:09.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the place!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:14.04,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:18.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Da… mn… Har… ri… ma… Ken… ji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:21.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Harima Kenji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:25.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The intonation is different…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:26.59,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:31.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Harry McKenzie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:34.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:38.15,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry McKenzie… Didn’t you\Ncall because you knew it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:44.01,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,However, young man, when asking\Na person’s name, give yours first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:46.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t that the manner of this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.87,0:05:49.78,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Haruki Hanai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:51.48,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’d like to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:53.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:58.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to settle it peacefully,\Nbut Japanese are belligerent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:01.63,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in danger of serious injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:03.03,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:07.70,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,They all have joints dislocated and\Nthere are some with back injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:10.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amateur fights wouldn’t end this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:12.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, are you saying this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:17.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That I assaulted\Nall these men by myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:20.04,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I wouldn’t go that far, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:22.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. That would be impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:26.32,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn’t have done that! Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:39.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have good reflexes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:41.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This guy…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:44.59,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute! There’s a lady watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.47,0:06:47.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanai-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:49.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y… Y… Y… Y… Yakumo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:53.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, there’s a good reason for this…\NBut, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:56.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, um… actually, my part-time job…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.41,0:06:58.75,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, it’s dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:00.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please step back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:01.98,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:05.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I’ll take you on,\Nyou dishonorable man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:08.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.19,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:12.86,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:18.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima… and Yakumo-kun on a date?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:20.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that’s not it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:25.04,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what are you here for?!\NIn this deserted back alley!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:26.84,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:28.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, actually…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:34.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Wait, Kenji! At this rate the\Nfact that I’m drawing manga will leak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:37.65,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, this is the last person\Nthat needs to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:41.48,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,To defeat you, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a wonderful goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:46.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll show you the result of my training!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:50.28,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, you have nothing\Nto do with this. Step back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.73,0:07:52.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the manuscript!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:55.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop there… Younger Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:59.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You pick it up! Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:05.96,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s a nice punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:09.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But it’s nothing, if you can’t connect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:13.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:18.99,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren’t I your opponent?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:21.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.70,0:08:26.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought there were no samurai\Nin this country, but… there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:28.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you finally realized it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.04,0:08:33.21,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter? Why do you falter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:37.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s too late for you to notice how terrible I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:42.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a samurai?! So this is sakayaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:42.37,note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an7}Sakayaki: shaving the forehead, samurai-style
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.89,0:08:44.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your cap…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:48.84,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This baldy is the one who stole your heart?
