Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.02,0:08:55.26,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that girl’s here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:58.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Gon-something-or-other from 2-D.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:08:59.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:01.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems she came to study from Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:04.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichi-jou!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:08.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m eating lunch with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:12.69,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that’s it, you practice\Nwrestling together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:15.69,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem very strong, Lala-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.69,0:09:19.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She challenged me to a match once,\Nthinking I was someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:22.19,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijou, that’s not a normal high school student conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:24.86,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So your name is Lala-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:26.79,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo, I’m taking this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:29.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichi-jou!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:29.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:32.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:33.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He is Imadori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:34.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:36.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Buzz off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.71,0:09:40.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t have to be so cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:41.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:46.81,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Her size is definitely…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:48.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,D!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:51.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:10:02.28,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um… that’s dangerous,\Nswinging that around…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:04.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn’t warrant something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:09.97,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.41,0:10:13.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:14.59,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a problem. Not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:17.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,One plus one is two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:21.01,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was saved by Ichijou, wasn’t I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:22.59,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:24.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish she stopped her sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.41,0:10:27.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Imadori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.59,0:10:33.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Miko-chin, she’s picking on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:33.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:35.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not “is that so?”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.87,0:10:37.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.43,0:10:39.86,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichi-jou, you like that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.81,0:10:42.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true, Ichijou?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.11,0:10:45.33,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve never… thought about it…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.78,0:10:48.78,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone as strong as you are,\Nwhat are you afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.78,0:10:51.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Take him by force! It’s irritating!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.12,0:10:54.28,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:57.26,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijou, tell us the details later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:11:02.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You with the big breasts!\NThis one’s way stronger than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:06.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Miko-chin, get her with your hyper-kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.40,0:11:08.56,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can take that blockhead\Nwith one blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:09.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:12.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch your mouth! I have nothing\Nto do with this, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:17.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are those in every country.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:19.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Worthless men and thieving women!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.91,0:11:20.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lala-san!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:23.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thieving women?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:29.65,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,My father was careless with women.\NWhen I see trash, it irritates me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:32.79,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You want a match?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:33.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:34.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.91,0:11:36.63,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that, even I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:43.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:45.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Claw!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:46.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What power!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:49.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.61,0:11:50.77,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:51.98,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:56.32,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Doowah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.85,0:11:58.68,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Doowah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:12:00.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:01.28,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mask, mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.89,0:12:13.17,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it fun picking on the weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:15.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:24.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, the two of you, cut…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:25.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don’t you cut it out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:28.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry McKenzie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:31.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s in the same school?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:34.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He not only took the words\Nout of my mouth, he has presence!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:36.15,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You’re…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:39.26,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him, Harry?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:41.65,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:46.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems there are pretexts involved.\NThis is interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:51.33,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I, chairman of 2-D, Masakazu Tougou,\Nhave a proposal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:58.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us, 2-D and 2-C students, settle all\Nour disagreements at the athletic meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:12:58.79,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:00.38,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:02.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I was going to propose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:08.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:09.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:13.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, are you okay, Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:23.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not fighting here, you are\Nan awful coward, Miko-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:32.45,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a shrew,\Njust as the rumors say!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.55,0:13:35.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren’t so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:37.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:38.26,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:39.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,These marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:45.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that’s it… I’ll look forward\Nto that athletic meet, Miko-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:46.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:48.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:51.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Banana?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:55.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s… it’s all over for me…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:57.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What size?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:14:00.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,About the same as Miko-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:01.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:03.38,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,A true man.
