Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:03.82,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1.2\be1\shad2\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs26\i1\c&HAE690B&\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\fscy115\pos(501,135)}www.mokkori.cz
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:07.84,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, you guys!\NThere’s a new nurse!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:10.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I heard she’s really good looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:11.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:15.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Already? First thing in the morning?!\NWhat’s with the get-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:17.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:19.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The place injured people\Ngo to is the infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:22.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t tell me… you hurt\Nyourselves for that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:27.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no regrets.\NThis is the way we live.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.23,0:14:33.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn… It’s uncomfortable going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:35.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody in class probably\Nknows about my bald spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.07,0:14:38.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,– The dressing’s coming off…\N– You’ve already been treated…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:41.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,They look like they’re gossiping!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:43.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:46.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I give up. I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.22,0:14:47.69,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going to rest in the infirmary!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.10,0:14:50.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn’t that Harima just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:53.76,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s going home already? I wonder why…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:56.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s acting just like a bad school girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:58.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be his head feels cool\Nand he can’t settle down?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:00.86,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:03.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shouldn’t you apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.87,0:15:08.10,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I apologized the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:09.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But it got worse, didn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.87,0:15:12.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Apologizing again would make things better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.88,0:15:14.04,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I absolutely don’t want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:17.21,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You are really stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:19.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Charming girls are frank, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:21.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, apologize, Eri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:23.81,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, geez! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.39,0:15:25.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.89,0:15:28.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Harima-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:30.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima-kun went to the infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:32.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?! Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.73,0:15:33.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.90,0:15:36.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:39.75,note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fax-0.2\bord0\frx16\fry328\frz22\c&H000000&\fnTahoma\move(306,136,259,136,0,2940)}Infirmary
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:38.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, is she there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.15,0:15:39.75,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.07,0:15:42.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we’ll play rock-paper-scissors to see who goes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:44.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to go in one at a time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:46.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t you know man-to-man is basic?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:48.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, what did they come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:50.17,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.75,0:15:51.26,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:56.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys again? I told you not\Nto make noise in the hallways!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:15:58.97,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, it’s Goriyama,\Nthe guidance counselor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:00.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:02.33,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ninjas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:05.17,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What’s the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:07.32,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot, what’s she doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:08.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:11.15,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:13.04,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukamoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:16.03,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave Tenma to me. I’ll get her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:20.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We can’t get in from the main entry…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:22.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,If that’s the case, let’s try from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.05,0:16:24.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,A new nurse?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:26.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.02,0:16:27.15,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:29.65,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,there was supposed to be a change\Nin the second semester.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.65,0:16:32.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The last one was a\Npleasant older lady, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:35.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t want to be seen\Napologizing to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:38.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. Hurry up and go in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:39.81,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:46.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-chan…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:52.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The window by the bed was left open.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.18,0:16:55.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there’s someone sleeping here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:17.70,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hario!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:19.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,How have you been!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:28.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He knocked down the nurse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:29.21,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,In the middle of the day?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:31.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,A delinquent does things\Ndifferent after all…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.55,0:17:33.69,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t ever go in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:43.25,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Boys are always chasing after girls
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:49.01,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,All day long they’re thinking of girls
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:53.71,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,But those boys certainly are a little stupid,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:59.18,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,They never seem to understand girls’ feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.63,0:18:03.80,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you really really are a big dummy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:06.47,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I give you a lesson, Big Dummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:09.86,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the most important thing in the world is…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:12.71,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that absolutely must be…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.71,0:18:17.15,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s definitely “timing”, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:20.29,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if you wanna say “I love you”,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:23.48,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on a date, or do something…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:29.49,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, kiss, or say goodbye, at any time…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:33.50,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the most important thing in the world is
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:38.41,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,definitely “timing”, I think, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:39.39,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Or something
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:56.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a grave state of affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:58.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,A student attacking faculty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:01.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a good thing it didn’t\Nbecome an incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:05.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Katou-sensei… It’s true that Harima has\Nbeen known to be quite a delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:08.98,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,However, he’s changed\Nsince he entered high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:12.35,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, it seems he’s found\Nsomething to devote himself to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:14.17,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t believe he’d do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:18.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tani-sensei! An indulgent educational\Nposture like that is a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:19.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:22.09,note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fax-0.2\bord0\frx16\fry328\frz22\c&H000000&\fnTahoma\pos(280,115)}Inﬁrmary
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.02,0:19:23.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anegasaki-sensei, we’re coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:25.98,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes, yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.36,0:19:28.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. Did you want something from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:31.52,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well, Harima from my class\Ncaused you great inconvenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:37.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t let it bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:41.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all my fault.\NHe’s not at fault at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.54,0:19:42.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is… is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:45.56,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than that…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.39,0:19:51.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I made cookies for the teachers,\Nto serve as a greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:53.21,note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.2\fs40\bord0\frz22\c&H000000&\fnTahoma\pos(291,147)\frx14\fry332}Faculty Room
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:19:58.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cookies?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:07.80,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tani-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:11.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuripe, what’s the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.10,0:20:17.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tani-san. Is it true\Nyou’re going to Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:22.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s something I want to give to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:25.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,These are cookies that I baked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:30.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuripe…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.64,0:20:41.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll eat them, later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.77,0:20:47.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The next day, and the day after that,\NGon gathered chestnuts—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.95,0:20:50.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, okay, that’s enough. Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:52.68,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you stop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:55.28,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re the one who should stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.18,0:20:59.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, everyone. My class is being noisy…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.54,0:21:01.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, you’re wrong there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:08.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We have been searching for opponents that can satisfy us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:11.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,When we meet them in the\Nupcoming athletic meet,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.06,0:21:13.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,we need them to be violent beasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:16.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichi-jou!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.34,0:21:18.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:21.97,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.94,0:21:25.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:29.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,2-D gives me stiff shoulders.\NClasses are easy, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.58,0:21:31.65,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.65,0:21:34.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anegasaki-sensei’s cookies will heal me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:46.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can’t find them anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:48.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard, Tani-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:51.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems my 2-D class and your 2-C
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.57,0:21:54.52,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,are competing with each other\Nat the athletic meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.84,0:21:56.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.44,0:22:02.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, between my superior class\Nand yours, we know which will win.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:04.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.08,0:22:06.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not me saying it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:08.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the gossip going\Naround within the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.42,0:22:11.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don’t be too harsh on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.22,0:22:12.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:15.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way, I had\Nthe cookies on your desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.53,0:22:19.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,They were sitting there forever,\Nso I thought you didn’t want them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.23,0:22:20.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.59,0:22:45.59,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Today’s class will be PE.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:48.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Change into your jerseys!\NWe’ll do some solid practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:52.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We will defeat Class 2-D.\NAim for the class championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:23:01.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Win… the athletic meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.38,0:23:07.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Tae Anegasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.95,0:23:09.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, do your best at the athletic meet, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:12.38,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get hurt, I’ll be waiting\Nin the infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.38,0:23:14.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next on School Rumble:
